prompt.title: Embedding for "Spotting Fake and Harmful Jewelry"
prompt.content:
---

In recent times of crisis, the market is increasingly flooded with fraudulent and harmful jewelry. Korálky Katlas has prepared a summary of key things to watch out for when purchasing ready-made jewelry and jewelry components, based on customer feedback and reported issues from both the Czech Republic and abroad.
